input.new_string:
/// How long an agent may go without any tool call before the registry treats
/// it as gone and prunes it (releasing its locks).
///
/// Tool calls are the only heartbeat the daemon sees - an interactive Claude
/// session is silent across the long gaps where the user is typing or the
/// model is generating text. A 5-minute threshold was short enough that two
/// agents on the same project would routinely fail to see each other
/// (whoever called `agent_list` during the other's quiet stretch saw an
/// incomplete roster, and `.panopt/agents.md` rewrote accordingly). 30
/// minutes covers any normal conversation pause without making the registry
/// effectively permanent.
const AGENT_MAX_IDLE: Duration = Duration::from_secs(1800);

